Package: Sequgio
Type: Package
Title: Isoform expression estimation based on RNA-seq data
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2015-02-19
Author: Suo Chen <chen.suo@ki.se>
Maintainer: Stefano Calza <stefano.calza@unibs.it>
Description: This package provides an algorithm to estimate isoforms expression from RNA-seq data based on a model that 
	     doesn't assume uniform distribution of count within transcripts.
	     Accessories function to import BAM data are also provided
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: R(>= 3.0.2), Rcpp(>= 0.11.1), RcppArmadillo(>= 0.4.100.2.1), nnls(>= 1.4), GenomicAlignments(>=
            0.99.32), bigmemory(>= 4.4.6), Rsamtools(>= 1.15.37), BiocParallel(>= 0.5.18), BH(>= 1.54.0-2),
	    data.table
Imports: AnnotationDbi, GenomicRanges,GenomicFeatures
Suggests: RNAseqData.HNRNPC.bam.chr14, TxDb.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19.knownGene
biocViews: DifferentialExpression, RNASeq, Sequencing, Software
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, bigmemory, BH
